abstract: "A production-grade, privacy-first open-source Electronic Health Record (EHR) and Clinical Decision Support System (CDSS) combining calibrated XGBoost diagnostic models, SHAP explainability, multi-agent LangGraph RAG, and native HL7 FHIR R4 interoperability."
